{"type": "article", "id": 30269, "title": "Gucci让开云很有面子，以及，这里有本关于篮球的独立杂志｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-29T02:39:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1548, "name": "开云集团"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 5170, "name": "Moncler"}, {"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 30083, "name": "CLIO"}, {"id": 30792, "name": "FRANCHISE"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160729103311JnLlKQ0t6uVi8vFg.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://119.90.25.23/www.kering.com/sites/default/files/kering_2016firsthalfreport_28july2016.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">这次拉动开云集团业绩的不仅有 Gucci 还有 Puma </a>｜本周四，开云集团发布 2016 年上半年财报，本财年第二季度比第一季度表现得更好。上半年，开云净收入上升 9.9%，达 5.19 亿美元，去年同期这个数字为 4.72 亿美元。除了 Gucci 拉动集团业绩增长外，表现得较好的品牌还有&nbsp;Puma 以及 Hedi Slimane 时代的 Saint Laurent 。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/dior-operating-profit-drops-in-second-half-10498330/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior 发布 2016 上半年财报，利润下降 30.2% 到 8250 万美元&nbsp;</a>｜Dior 表示业绩下滑是很大程度是受了“游客的影响”。“我们在一些地方市场销售有所增长，但是不足以弥补巴黎游客减少引起的业绩下滑。”Dior 首席执行官&nbsp;Sidney Toledano 说。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/moncler-first-half-2016-sales-10497368/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moncler 2016 年上半年收入上涨 17%</a>｜根据其发布的半年财报，收入为 3.88 亿美元。在伦敦的旗舰店之后，今年下半年其在首尔和纽约等的 9 个旗舰店将开业。其在中国和日本市场的收入都超过了平均水平。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/advertising/tiffany-first-luxury-brand-buy-a-snapchat-lens-10497684/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tiffany 在 Snapchat 上做了一个滤镜</a>&nbsp;｜简单说来就是在使用 Snapchat 时，可以加上蓝色或者白色的心型。这个滤镜只在&nbsp;Snapchat 上存在 24 小时，目前只有美国、澳大利亚、意大利的用户可以使用，也是 Tiffany 主要在社交媒体上做的营销&nbsp; #LoveNotLike。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">LVMH 集团用 5 千万美元投资的韩妆品牌 Clio 推出了一种新型 BB cushion，名为 The Kill Cover Stamping Foundation。特点是粉饼长得像印章，一面的设计平滑，另一面是流线型曲线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729094041GOXP81rJ4IkvC96V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.853333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729094109mLAKH6S9sf2lqOpw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729094117bvoBySdhMNKckTln.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/resort-2017/new-york/tommy-hilfiger/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;Tommy Hilfiger 推出 2017 年度假系列</a>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728165222nRXwxFDJ5BhqUYM4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.506836\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728165337SLzODcQkelXEnCKG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.506836\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728165656kUf17CvEKIGZNJwP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507813\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728170202sLj1FY46DNuKXxkG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507813\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728170234yzoKMbBWjfDTwP7p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.506836\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Adidas 全新推出的超级粉嫩的 adidas EQT Support ADV，网面设计，鞋子用绑带巧妙“取代”的品牌的标志性三条杠。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728223001SmQd3obA7y9ZvzUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728223012myw0N4skO7eu5zcW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728223038IlQNOoKwt6xpsz4W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/vetements-2016-fall-collection-lookbook-matches-fashion\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements 发布 2016 年秋冬 lookbook 。</a><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728223805nqUYGb8m6Hg9aSjt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607282238243Xe6yIdhoPS2m1qu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728223842vwegF1jdybMRIlrJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607282240058DIXKbga2Lh5SwOr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728224016HczlVFtfGnWI7Uqk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/franchise-basketball-blog-print\" rel=\"nofollow\">介绍一本刚推出的关于篮球的独立杂志 FRANCHISE 。</a>有趣之处在于这本纸质印刷物是从其博客上内容转化而来，内容以篮球主题，用摄影和图像的方式介绍全球各地和篮球相关的艺术家、音乐和设计师。有兴趣可以去它的官网看看，<a href=\"https://thisisfranchise.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729094835KvcN1UfVjGL03hJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729094916ZbjGDVSkI4NfX2El.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729094926LyFS9QOVc4wAE8Bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729094953cq6HJNE1tI3ngi7w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729095001gUSdGTHs3JVrNjaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729095009EqhRI49DKmvPe7Cj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729095022L8cG2ta3oZjFRT0A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160729095047esvF3N0kLoqm5h6a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>"}